OL,3,CPlaid Cymru secures the most seats in
OL,4,Chistoric Senedd Election
OL,6,FIn a historic first, Plaid Cymru have
OL,7,Fwon the most seats of any party in the
OL,8,FSenedd Election.
OL,10,FThe party holds 43 seats, followed by
OL,11,FReform UK who have 34. It is the first
OL,12,Ftime in history a party other than
OL,13,FLabour have had the largest amount of
OL,14,FSenedd seats.
OL,16,FPlaid Cymru's Leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,17,Fsaid: "Today it has become clear that
OL,18,FWales demanded that change of
OL,19,Fleadership."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
