OL,3,CPlaid Cymru secures the most seats in
OL,4,Chistoric Senedd Election
OL,6,FAlthough they are now the largest
OL,7,Fparty in the Senedd, Plaid do not have
OL,8,Fenough members to form a majority
OL,9,Fgovernment. To get an outright
OL,10,Fmajority, any party needed at least 49
OL,11,Fseats.
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru could now look to do a
OL,14,Fdeal with MSs from other parties, to
OL,15,Fgain their support.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
