OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1778501468
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru secures the most seats in
OL,4,Chistoric Senedd Election
OL,6,FA possible deal between Plaid Cymru
OL,7,Fand another party or MSs could take
OL,8,Fthe form of a coalition - where two or
OL,9,Fmore parties enter government
OL,10,Ftogether, forming a cabinet and taking
OL,11,Fjoint responsibility for decisions.
OL,13,FAnother option is a cooperation
OL,14,Fagreements, which is less formal than
OL,15,Fa coalition but based around a
OL,16,Fprogramme of government. It could also
OL,17,Flook like a "supply and confidence"
OL,18,Farrangement, whereby one or more
OL,19,Fsmaller parties agree to support or
OL,20,Fabstain in a government's budget vote.
