OL,3,CPlaid Cymru secures the most seats in
OL,4,Chistoric Senedd Election
OL,6,FPlaid has previously worked in
OL,7,Farrangements with Welsh Labour, but
OL,8,Fthis was when Labour held the most
OL,9,FSenedd seats.
OL,11,FIn 2007, Plaid Cymru formed a
OL,12,Fcoalition with Labour, who had fallen
OL,13,Ffour seats short of a majority,
OL,14,Fresulting in the One Wales government.
OL,15,FMore recently, after the last Senedd
OL,16,FElection, Plaid signed a three-year
OL,17,Fcooperation deal with Welsh Labour.
OL,18,FThis meant they agreed to work
OL,19,Ftogether in certain areas of policy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
